Interface VerificationUnit

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    VerificationUnitImpl

    public interface VerificationUnit
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Verification Unit'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Model
    • Specification
    • Viewpoint
    • Component
    • Name

    See Also:
    VerifiersPackage.getVerificationUnit()
